    {'Type': 'Special', 'Name': 'Journal Entry, First', 'Weight': '0.09', 'BuyValue': '1,000 G', 'SellValue': '12 G', 'ForgeryCost': '1,500 G', 'Craftable': '', 'Combinableitem': '', 'Enhancingitem': '', 'img': 'resources/images/Journal Entry, First.png', 'desc': 'First Journal Entry is an item available in Dragon\'s Dogma. "An excerpt torn from a traveler\'s daybook. It outlines the author\'s decision to set out on a journey. \'Tis with heavy heart I leave hearth and home behind, but vengeance must be dealt. The beast what struck the village and stole away my dear Alicia will die by my hand." The first part of a journal written by Reynard\'s father as one of a set of six: First Journal Entry, Second Journal Entry, Third Journal Entry, Fourth Journal Entry, Fi', 'ID': 190, 'id': 190},
    {'Type': 'Special', 'Name': 'Journal Entry, Second', 'Weight': '0.09', 'BuyValue': '1,000 G', 'SellValue': '32 G', 'ForgeryCost': '1,500 G', 'Craftable': '', 'Combinableitem': '', 'Enhancingitem': '', 'img': 'resources/images/Journal Entry, Second.png', 'desc': 'Second Journal Entry is an item available in Dragon\'s Dogma. "An excerpt torn from a traveler\'s daybook. It documents the unearthing of treasure in unnamed ruins. Word of the beast led me to this cave. A week\'s searching has seen ancient treasure unearthed, but what use have I for baubles? \'Tis only vengeance for my daughter I seek." The second part of a journal written by Reynard\'s father as one of a set of six: First Journal Entry, Second Journal Entry, Third Journal Entry, Fourth Journal Entr', 'ID': 191, 'id': 191},
